scan_owncloud.py

Phase 1: Peter J Ryan Photography – ownCloud Folder Scanner

Connects to Peter’s ownCloud instance via WebDAV and walks the
“Peter’s Photos” directory, outputting:

1. A human-readable tree report  (output/folder_report.txt)
1. A machine-readable JSON file  (output/folder_structure.json)

These outputs are used to decide which folders/files to include
or exclude before building the photo pipeline and website.

