1. Make sure a .env file exists in the SAME folder (see .env.example).
1. In Spyder’s IPython console, install dependencies once:
   pip install requests python-dotenv
1. Open this file in Spyder and press F5 (or click Run) to execute.
1. Check the output/ subfolder for folder_report.txt and
   folder_structure.json.
